import React from 'react' import { Autocomplete } from '@react-google-maps/api' import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography, InputBase, Box, Grid } from '@material-ui/core' import SearchIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Search' import useStyles from './styles.js' import { useState } from 'react' import TravelExploreTwoToneIcon from '@mui/icons-material/TravelExploreTwoTone'; const Header = ({ setCoordinates }) => { const classes = useStyles(); const [autocomplete, setAutocomplete] = useState(null); const onLoad = (autoC) => setAutocomplete(autoC); const onPlaceChanged = () => { const lat = autocomplete.getPlace().geometry.location.lat(); const lng = autocomplete.getPlace().geometry.location.lng(); setCoordinates({ lat, lng }); } return ( {/* Your Name */} {/* TravelMate */} Explore new places
) } export default Header
